{
  "stem": "16473.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- the only Jewish religious leadership I got at that time from my parents was because my dad was the manager of JOIN.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they had a group Passover dinner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was the youngest, and I was to ask the four questions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I hated Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I told you, I didn't know any Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so my mother phonetically typed out the four questions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I'm holding up this book and, with great feeling, asking the four questions, to the point where the rabbi said to my parents, you know, this child is very talented, you should do something, and so on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the next night I refused to go because it was sham.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I did not want to participate in it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was left home by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They went and I was left home, but I felt very strongly about that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The experiences I had after the war, I think, maybe shook me up more than the experiences during the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know why that is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I have a feeling it's so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'd walk across a playground and see the-- I'm laughing because you can't see me do this-- but the cut-off leg of some person.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'd go like-- you know, what is this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I came in contact, about as much contact as I was going to, with the meaning of man's inhumanity to man, by seeing it and smelling it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that made a big, big impression on me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Even the fact that the horses were being slaughtered for food, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Didn't seem right to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But anyway, in school, I don't remember being discriminated against, as you say.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
